ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 2 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2016-1 (Dakota Plains)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 2 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, NO. 2016-1 (DAKOTA PLAINS) in order to add the name of the Province of Manitoba, the name of Dakota Plains, an Indian band situated in Manitoba, the name of the band's council and the description of the reserves where the provincial-type tax could apply.
